Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:15.60,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's move on to the next quest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:18.24,Haganai 01,Yukimura,0000,0000,0000,,One.{Senna: I'm aware of the lead-in here and perhaps in the next 3 lines too, but seeing as the girls are counting in rhythm, I decided to just keep these four lines the same length.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:18.74,Haganai 01,Kobato,0000,0000,0000,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:19.24,Haganai 01,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:19.74,Haganai 01,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:33.84,Haganai 01,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:36.24,Haganai 01,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.76,Haganai 01,Kobato,0000,0000,0000,,You actually aren't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:25.30,Haganai 02,Karaoke,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow will surely be filled with surprises,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:27.84,Haganai 02,Karaoke,0000,0000,0000,,so let's go and find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:31.20,Haganai 02,Karaoke,0000,0000,0000,,The sun shines brilliantly in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:35.81,Haganai 02,Karaoke,0000,0000,0000,,Let's draw a sketch of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:43.62,Haganai 02,Karaoke,0000,0000,0000,,For always standing next to me, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:46.93,Haganai 02,Karaoke,0000,0000,0000,,As we go towards tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:51.45,Haganai 02,Karaoke,0000,0000,0000,,let's sketch our smiles together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:53.77,Haganai 02,Karaoke,0000,0000,0000,,This smiling moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:57.62,Haganai 02,Karaoke,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}draw it for me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:08.65,Haganai 01,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,Kodaka-senpai, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:10.16,Haganai 01,Yukimura,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Aniki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:14.15,Haganai 01,Kobato,0000,0000,0000,,Here, An-chan! You should eat it with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.73,Haganai 01,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you can eat mine as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:28.83,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,Kodaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:32.34,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,Kodaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:49.20,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:50.83,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,My victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.35,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Kodaka, you're too strong.{Senna: Too little gap between scene change and start of the line, so I'm letting the lead-in go to avoid too much "flashing"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.85,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,That's to be expected of Kodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:57.00,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.23,Haganai 01,Yukimura,0000,0000,0000,,Aniki's existence truly is magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:02.09,Haganai 01,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, that was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.51,Haganai 01,Kobato,0000,0000,0000,,Just as expected of my An-chan!{Senna: Same idea with too little of a gap between scene change and the start of this line to pick on the lead-in...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.33,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.26,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}IRL fulfillment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.85,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}sure feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:16.01,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm getting hungry. Let's have some food soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.95,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea. The hot pot's all ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.24,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why hot pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.57,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to summer retreats, hot pots are a must!{wording}{Senna: How about "During summer retreats, hot pot is a must!" or "... hot pots are a must!"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.20,Haganai 01,Yukimura,0000,0000,0000,,It is just as she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:28.28,Haganai 01,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Hot pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.73,Haganai 01,Kobato,0000,0000,0000,,Hot pot, hot pot! Let's eat!{Senna: Same small gap, let lead-in live thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:34.34,Haganai 01,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai. Senpai. Please wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:37.00,Haganai 01,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai. Please come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.70,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,What am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:58.49,Haganai 01,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,Tried to escape to your own private world, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:01.01,Haganai 01,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,How unfair, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:03.65,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,I was having... such lovely hallucinations...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.45,Haganai 01,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of hallucinations?{ya know, the one where you see things}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:10.87,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,For example, Yozora and Sena getting along and playing together at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.26,Haganai 01,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the unscientific scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:14.83,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:20.40,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you started feeling the pain by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.59,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you surrender for your own sake, Meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.87,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,How about you give up instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:28.33,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,Your breathing is getting heavier, woman-fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.38,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,S-Spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.90,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.70,Haganai 02,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,The inside of my mouth is getting sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.92,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:44.48,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:47.75,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,to make sure we don't embarrass ourselves when we have hot pot parties with friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:49.70,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,let's have a rehearsal hot pot party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.35,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, wouldn't Mystery Hot Pot fit the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.46,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Seems kinda fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.59,Haganai 01,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:56.71,Haganai 01,Yukimura,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.34,Haganai 02,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:05:59.57,Haganai 02,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery Hot Pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:06:01.13,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you have Mystery Hot Pot when trying to make friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.62,Haganai 01,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:07.84,Haganai 01,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,the Devil... he cometh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:10.43,Haganai 01,Yukimura,0000,0000,0000,,Move away, An-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.60,Haganai 01,Yukimura,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:14.44,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Maria... Kobato...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.54,Haganai 02,Yukimura,0000,0000,0000,,Aniki... Aniki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:17.41,Haganai 01,Yukimura,0000,0000,0000,,Aniki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.33,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yukimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.66,Haganai 01,Yukimura,0000,0000,0000,,Aniki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:25.40,Haganai 01,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,The closest thing to this foodstuff in Rika's memory database would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.11,Haganai 01,Rika,0000,0000,0000,,rubbing alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:32.76,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Rika! You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.73,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,On to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:36.36,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.01,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.40,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.49,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is the story...{Senna: I'm hearing "Kore ha... totemo zannen na..." at the start of this little reflection from Kodaka, and then in line 154, Kodaka says "zannen" again, and that's where "pathetic" was chosen to be used... I'm just wondering why it wasn't put in at this line... Maybe something like "This... is the pathetic story..." blah blah... "the story of an extremely pathetic everyday life." just to emphasize how pathetic the entire scenario is for Kodaka? I don't know... ><}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.76,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a story that starts with both heroines vomiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:19.57,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the story of an extremely pathetic everyday life.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:59.46,0:09:03.07,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, with the goal in mind
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.91,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,of accruing good relationships with those in our vicinity,
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.91,0:09:10.13,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,we will help and encourage each other
Dialogue: 2,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.24,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,while developing our bodies and minds,
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.24,0:09:15.40,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,so that we may not infringe upon the trust of others
Dialogue: 2,0:09:15.99,0:09:19.08,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,until we go toward ends of our own.{Senna: "toward" instead of "towards", since "we" is plural? And if you agree, please reflect the change in the typeset versions of this "line"! ^^}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.42,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,The Neighbors Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:02.20,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm really liking this song and animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.73,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not {\i1}bad{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:06.51,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a way to make it even more perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:07.27,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.37,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know, Kodaka? It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.32,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,Erase Meat from both the visuals and the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:13.52,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,What are you blabbering on about, Yozora?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.55,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,If I weren't here, this show would be worth nothing!{Senna: "weren't" instead of "wasn't"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.36,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it would be worth less than nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.00,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,What's worth less than nothing is your own existence, Meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.28,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a goddess such as me could be worth that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:25.59,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, how about having just me on screen and doing the singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:29.02,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,That's a guaranteed chart-topper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.86,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,A mere piece of Meat shouldn't joke about "chart-topping".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:35.35,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,Chill off in the cooler and understand your nothingness.{Senna: I cut this line early for the scene change, and gave the next line the subsequent tiny lead in, as I felt this scene change and line change was too "flashy"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:36.78,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,Why the refrigerator?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:40.85,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not understand my graciousness in preventing you from rotting and stinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.44,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,However you look at it, that's not being gracious at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.76,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, do I get a part in the song?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:46.91,Haganai 01,Sena/Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way in hell you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:47.57,Haganai 01,Kodaka,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:06.79,Haganai 01,Yozora,0000,0000,0000,,So, Meat, you ended up playing games the whole time.{Senna: Scene flashing in from black and then subs flashing in... I'll go with the lead-in ><}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.34,Haganai 01,Sena,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did not!
